::Striker/Mosquitor::

Striker runs up to near DarkMouse, looking at Suukie. He weapons were fully 
armed: shoulder blasters out and two guns in his hands.

"Is he allright?" he asks, looking from DarkMouse to Suukie.

"DIE MAXIMALS!!!!" Is heard as Mosquitor flies into view, shooting acid at 
DarkMouse, Striker, and Mosquitor.
